article_title: Habitat for Humanity celebrates new home
article_text: Reading Eagle: Harold Hoch | Habitat for Humanity of Berks County celebrates a new home Saturday as Executive Director Timothy J. Daley, right, presents a ceremonial key to homeowners Sandra Saldana Romero, left, and her daughter Yeslee Saldana in the 400 block of Pearl Street.
